ebelius home women great the essence of good government is trust kathleen sebelius trust good government but for us democrats obamacare is a badge of honor because no matter who you are what stage of life youre in this law is a good thing kathleen sebelius life good law more than five million seniors have already saved money on their prescription drugs and almost  million have benefited from free preventive services the president cracked down hard on medicare and health care fraud recovering a recordbreaking  billion over the last three years protecting our seniors thats what change looks like kathleen sebelius change money health and under obamacare insurance companies can no longer discriminate against women before some wouldnt cover womens most basic needs like contraception and maternity care but would still charge us up to  percent more than men  for a worse plan kathleen sebelius women men care being a mother is no longer a liability and being a woman is no longer a preexisting condition kathleen sebelius mother woman being theres a digital revolution taking place both in and out of government in favor of opensourced data innovation and collaboration kathleen sebelius innovation collaboration while closing our innovation gaps wont solve all our problems we have some very real opportunities to improve the quality of care thats delivered to millions of americans kathleen sebelius innovation quality what weve been finding is that when you remove the barriers to innovation you can actually hold costs down while lifting entrepreneurs up and getting better health results kathleen sebelius health innovation better weve been finding that when you empower engineers scientists and coders they respond by creating new tools to empower physicians patients and parents kathleen sebelius parents tools empower global health issues remind us  perhaps more than any other issue  that we are all children of the same extended family kathleen sebelius family health children in many ways human health is the great global connector kathleen sebelius health great human in this st century world some of our countrys most significant exports and imports extend beyond goods and services they also include innovation knowledge discovery and healing kathleen sebelius knowledge innovation world i know how tough it is to stand up to powerful forces that prey on consumers kathleen sebelius powerful know tough although black and white americans live work and learn together now there is still injustice in america kathleen sebelius work black and white black a healthy state encourages many voices  and lots of listening kathleen sebelius listening healthy voices but the dollars spent on economic incentives and new investment strategies are wasted unless we seriously address the two most important economic issues in kansas education and health care kathleen sebelius education health care but wishing our kansas soldiers god speed is not enough we need to comfort care for and protect their families and we should ease the financial burdens that these families often face kathleen sebelius god financial care i believe we all agree that for the health of kansas nothing is more important than education kathleen sebelius education health believe if your voices are not heard you can be sure that many others will be  in particular those who are paid to present a point of view and often do it most effectively kathleen sebelius view you present we have by far the most expensive health system in the world we spend  percent more per person than the next most costly nation americans spend more on health care than housing or food kathleen sebelius food health world general motors spends more on health care than steel kathleen sebelius health care more insurance companies can no longer refuse to cover americans with preexisting conditions thats what change looks like kathleen sebelius change insurance looks being a mother is no longer a liability and being a woman is no longer a