riendly products as part of a joint effort the kansas department of health and environment launched the get caught recycling contest in  in  sebelius vetoed legislation intended to overturn the administrations rejection of permits for two coalfired power plants in western kansas proponents of the legislation claimed that vetoing the bill would mean higher energy costs for kansans months later sebelius called for a stronger federal commitment to renewable energy sources while speaking at an american wind energy association conference firearms sebelius vetoed concealed carry laws in  and  claiming while every lawabiding kansan has a right to keep and bear arms hidden weapons make it harder for law enforcement to do its job and they make kansas workplaces less safe in  sebelius signed into law a bill legalizing the possession of fully automatic weapons which had been banned since  the bill mainly benefited collectors and dealers delivering weapons to law enforcement agencies samesex marriage sebelius did not support an april  amendment to the kansas constitution that made samesex marriage in the state unconstitutional sebelius said she supported the existing state law outlawing samesex marriage viewed it as sufficient and therefore opposed the constitutional amendment the amendment passed with  percent voter approval analysis department budget us department of health and human services annual budget yearbudget in billions difference from previous yearna note  only represents the departments budget request not an enacted budget net worth see also changes in net worth of us senators and representatives personal gain index and net worth of united states senators and representatives  based on congressional financial disclosure forms and calculations made available by opensecretsorg sebelius net worth as of  was estimated between  and  that averages to  which ranks th among executive branch members personal she is married to gary sebelius a federal magistrate judge with whom she has two sons recent news this section displays the most recent stories in a google news search for the term kathleen  sebelius  secretary  health  human  services kathleen sebelius news feed loading external links social media twitter biographies nndb wikipedia political profiles project vote smart factchecking politifact financial federal level opensecretsorg legistormcom interest group ratings project vote smart issue positions on the issues project vote smart public statements project vote smart voting record project vote smart works by or about worldcat media appearances imdb media coverage bloomberg new york times washington post footnotes ↑   cnn sebelius sworn in as health and human services secretary april   ↑ new york times health secretary resigns after woes of healthcaregov april   ↑   ny times sebelius said to weigh run for kansas senate seat accessed april   ↑    ny times sebelius says she’s not interested in senate run accessed april   ↑      us department of health and human services biography hhs secretary accessed june   ↑ governing former ohio gov gilligan dies august   ↑   biographycom kathleen sebelius biography accessed june   ↑ govtrack on the nomination april   ↑ christianscience monitor how john roberts upheld healthcare law while limiting congressional power june   ↑ christianscience monitor hobby lobby  explaining the supreme courts birth control ruling july   ↑ politico when barry met kathy december   ↑ politico jay carney pushes back on kathleen sebelius report december   ↑ the hill before ocare debacle sebelius made many trips to white house february   ↑ chicago tribune computer glitches overloads hit health care exchanges october   ↑ bloomberg insurers getting faulty data from us health exchanges october   ↑ politico another obstacle to signing up for aca crops up october   ↑ pittsburgh tribunereview sebelius visit fails to reassure as health care website glitches persist october   ↑ youtube senator roberts call for secretary sebe